Author: Nexchange.co.uk
Title: [ANN][ICO] n.exchange launches ICO
Body: One of the components of the n.exchange Eco-System is the Merchant solution. This merchant solution is available for traditional-economy enterprises to get paid with cryptocurrency and receive fiat, a different cryptocurrency, or any combination of the original payment currency with the aforementioned. Another aspect to this solution is enabling multi-currency payments for the purpose of ICO.  We are happy to announce that we are planning to deploy our solution to be used on our own ICO (naturally). This solution also has fiat & KYC integration, but for now, for regulatory and ideological reasons we do not intend to accept local (fiat) currency as part of our crowd-sale.  To summarize that, every currency that is supported by the n.exchange API under the following endpoint would be accepted during the public sale, whilst the private sale would be confined to ETH only. https://api.nexchange.io/en/admin/core/currency/  API documentation can be found below https://nexchange2.docs.apiary.io/

Body: PRE-SALE STARTS ON JULY 15TH 2018  MAIN SALE STARTS ON SEPTEMBER 15TH 2018, ENDS ON OCTOBER 16TH 2018   _____________________________________________________________________   Join The ICO: N.EXCHANGE/ICO  Sign Up for the Airdrop: LINK TO AIRDROP  Join the Bounty Program: LINK TO BOUNTY  Working Product: TRY OUR INSTANT EXCHANGE   _____________________________________________________________________   Try our product   We believe that the success of our ICO, as well as of our live product depends largely on the strength of our community. For this reason, we will grant community members who have used our product one additional free lottery ticket to our NEX AirDrop, in case of completing at least one order a week on average until the lottery occurs (1st of August). For the same reason, we will add a bonus of 50% for bounty hunters that comply with the same terms!  For community members that will participate in our crowd-sale, we will offer 50% of their fees back via free nex tokens, additionally to any pre-sale/public sale bonus, and up to 50% of their entire purchased amount, without bonuses!   Learn about the project  WHITEPAPER EN | ONEPAGER EN | PRODUCT HUNT | BETA LIST | BETA LAUNCH STORY | SET UP YOUR OWN EXCHANGE   _______________________________________________________________________________ ________   Our Vision   Dear customers and crowdsale participants,  From the very beginning the idea behind N.EXCHANGE was to establish a platform that customers can fully trust. One that is designed to have no conflict of interest with the client and which has the potential to become the first, regulated, A-Book broker in the crypto sphere.  We have designed our system to have the smallest possible attack surface and, where possible, to take no custody of customer funds, whatsoever.  We strongly believe that, in order for this sphere to prosper, one of the key principles of the newly-minted crypto economy, decentralization, must prevail.  Therefore, we encourage every customer to take custody of their own funds, and to use the variety of services we offer to exchange cryptocurrency, fiat or goods, using the merchant solution; and to mine or remit cryptocurrency, all under one roof, securely, transparently, and with zero transmission time. Author: Nexchange.co.uk
Title: [ANN][ICO] n.exchange launches ICO
Body: Good afternoon.  We are a team of Bitcoin maximalists with many years of experience in the sphere. Our vision is that for Bitcoin to prosper and to become as big as the major NYSE stocks at first, and bigger than fiat currencies later, institutional money must be involved.  Current exchanges simply do not offer what institutional investors need: - Insurance for funds in custody - Advanced, regulatory-compliant reporting - HFT-ready API with the needed security measures in place, oAuth2 for different permissions for different roles  Via HybriDEX, We offer a balanced, hybrid solution that combines transparent, cryptographically-provable fiat trading with some advantages of the old-money world: insurance, regulation, audit, bank-level IT security.

Author: Alwelldinho5
Title: [ANN][ICO] n.exchange launches ICO
Body: With n.exchange you receive a final quote for your trade prior to completing the transaction. This quote will include all fees and will be valid for 15 minutes after being issued, at no additional charge.  This is such a unique feature that  is still unsure how to quantify it – especially since it is well-known that the cryptocurrency market can move very quickly within this period of time.

Author: Alwelldinho5
Title: [ANN][ICO] n.exchange launches ICO
Body: n.exchange strives to perform all exchange operations in a decentralised manner and with minimum custody of customer funds. The system is designed to encourage customers to take custody of their own funds, and only to deposit those funds, into the hands of the exchange, when they intend do so, in full conscience.  This proposed approach is in complete contrast to the industry’s current (common) practice, where customers are led to deposit their funds by default, and where with- drawing those funds is made as difficult as possible.  This is one of our strongest product principles - we call it ZeroBalance.  Although ZeroBalance is quantifiable to only 0, we strongly believe that this principle is one of our strongest value propositions. We also believe that it will protect the dig- ital wealth of our customers, far beyond anything our competitors can offer.
